This is the package "ecrc-procir" for generating CRC journal articles using the Elsevier LaTeX document class elsarticle.
The package incorporates customisations for the Elsevier CRC journal 
Procedia CIRP
This version 1.0 dated 19 March 2018
************************************************************

The following files are included:
* The elsarticle document class, elsarticle.cls
* The documentation, elsdoc.pdf
* A bibliographic style file for the havard reference style, elsarticle-harv.bst
* The package file for Elsevier CRC, ecrc.sty
* Sample journal logo files elsevier-logo-5p, SDlogo-5p (in PDF and PS format)
(All the above are also available at http://www.elsevier.com/latex)

* A template manuscript file, procir-template-LANE-2018.tex

To use:
1. Unpack all the files into the same folder
2. Edit the manuscript file procir-template-LANE-2018.tex according to the instructions in that file, and save with a new name
3. Compile with PDFLaTeX or LaTeX (and BibTeX if desired)


**************************************************************
*                                                            *
* Important note on usage                                    *
* -----------------------                              	     *
* Files using ecrc should normally be compiled with PDFLaTeX *
* Using standard LaTeX should work, but may produce clashes  *
*                                                            *
**************************************************************



